    "title": "Bekendtgørelse om ændring af bekendtgørelse om salmonella hos svin",
    "documentTypeId": "80",
    "isSagsforlobPeriodValid": true,
    "shortName": "BEK nr 1127 af 02/12/2011",
    "documentHtml": "<div class=\"bjelke\">Oversigt (indholdsfortegnelse)</div><table class=\"Indholdsfortegnelse\">\r\n   <tr>\r\n      <td class=\"IndholdsfortegnelseId\">\r\n         <a href=\"#Bil1\">Bilag 1</a>\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td class=\"IndholdsfortegnelseTekst\">\r\n      </td>\r\n   </tr>\r\n</table><div class=\"bjelke\">Den fulde tekst</div><p class=\"Titel2\">Bekendtgørelse om ændring af bekendtgørelse om salmonella hos svin</p>\r\n<p class=\"CentreretParagraf\">§ 1</p>\r\n<p class=\"Tekst2\">I bekendtgørelse nr. 1722 af 22. december 2010 om salmonella hos svin foretages følgende ændringer:</p>\r\n<p class=\"AendringMedNummer\">\r\n   <span class=\"AendringNr\">1.</span> Overalt i bekendtgørelsen ændres »fødevareregionen« og »fødevareregionens« til henholdsvis »Fødevarestyrelsen« og »Fødevarestyrelsens«.</p>\r\n<p class=\"AendringMedNummer\">\r\n   <span class=\"AendringNr\">2.</span> <span class=\"Italic\">§ 18, stk. 6 </span>affattes således:</p>\r\n<p class=\"Stk2\">  <span class=\"Italic\">»Stk. 6</span>. Den ansvarlige for virksomheden skal sikre, at resultatet af overvågningen for den pågældende måned indberettes senest 14 dage inde i den efterfølgende måned. Indberetningen af serotypen kan dog ske, når den foreligger. Indberetningen sker til Fødevarestyrelsen efter styrelsens anvisninger.«</p>\r\n<p class=\"AendringMedNummer\">\r\n   <span class=\"AendringNr\">3.</span> <span class=\"Italic\">§ 29</span> affattes således:</p>\r\n<p class=\"Stk2\">  <span class=\"Bold\">»§ 29.</span> Laboratoriet skal straks indberette enhver bakteriologisk eller serologisk påvisning af salmonellabakterier eller antistoffer mod salmonella i prøver udtaget efter reglerne i § 3, stk. 2 og 4, § 4, § 10, stk. 4, § 15 eller § 17, til Fødevarestyrelsen.«</p>\r\n<p class=\"AendringMedNummer\">\r\n   <span class=\"AendringNr\">4.</span> <span class=\"Italic\">Bilag 9</span> affattes som bilag 1 til denne bekendtgørelse.</p>\r\n<p class=\"CentreretParagraf\">§ 2</p>\r\n<p class=\"Stk2\">\r\n   <span class=\"StkNr\">\r\n   </span> Bekendtgørelsen træder i kraft den 8. december 2011.</p><div class=\"Givet\" id=\"Givet\"><p class=\"Givet\" align=\"center\">Fødevarestyrelsen, den 2. december 2011</p><p class=\"Sign1\" align=\"center\">Esben Egede Rasmussen</p><p class=\"Sign2\" align=\"right\">/ Rikke Karlsson</p></div><a id=\"B1\">\r\n   <hr class=\"BilagStreg\" />\r\n</a>\r\n<p class=\"Bilag\">\r\n   <span id=\"Bil1\">Bilag 1</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Bilagstekst\" style=\"text-align: right;\">\r\n   <span class=\"Bold\">»Bilag 9</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"Bilagstekst\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n   <span class=\"Bold\">Overvågning af kritisk resistent salmonella</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n   <div style=\"width:100%\">\r\n      <table class=\"Containertable\" style=\"border-style: none; border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px;\">\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border-style: none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n               <table valign=\"top\" class=\"Maintable\" align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"SchultzColumns: 170 170 170 170;\" width=\"680\">\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-top: 0.018cm solid #000000text-align: center\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">Prøvetype</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-top: 0.018cm solid #000000text-align: center\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">Prøveregi</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-top: 0.018cm solid #000000text-align: center\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">Udtagningssted</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-right: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-top: 0.018cm solid #000000text-align: center\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">Prøveudtager</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-right: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">Kortlægning, </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">stibundsprøver</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">§ 10, stk. 4, § 15 </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">samt bilag 3</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Avls-, opformerings- </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">og sobesætninger</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-right: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">En dyrlæge eller efter </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">dyrlægens anvisning og under dennes ansvar.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">DANMAP, </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">blindtarmsprøver</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Aftale med branchen iht. den fjerde </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Slagteriet</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-right: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Slagteriet</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">salmonellahandlingsplan (SHIV), Blindtarmsprøver, som udtages blandt tilfældigt valgte slagtesvin til DANMAP, undersøges for kritisk resistente salmonella </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-right: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">Velfærdsbesøg og medicinkontrol, stibundsprøver</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Stibundsprøver, som udtages fra alle slagtesvinebesætninger, </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Slagtesvinebesætninger</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-right: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Fødevarestyrelsen/ </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">NaturErhvervstyrelsen</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">der udvælges til velfærds- og medicinbesøg. Prøveudtagningen afvikles i regi af Central Koordinerede Laboratorieprojekter (CKL)</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-right: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">Ferskkødsovervågning</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">§ 18 og bilag 7</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Slagteriet</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-right: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Slagteriet</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">Eksportundersøgelser</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Stikprøvekontrol af færdigpakket fersk kød </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Slagteriet og opskæringsvirksomheden </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-right: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Slagteriet og opskæringsvirksomheden</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">forud for eksport til Sverige og Finland. Bestemmelser er fastsat i Kommissionens forordning nr. 1688/2005 af 14. oktober 2005 om gennemførelse af Europa-Parlamentets og Rådets forordning (EF) nr. 853/2004 for så vidt angår særlige garantier vedrørende salmonella for sendinger til Finland og Sverige af visse typer kød og æg.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding-left: 0.249cm; padding-right: 0.249cm; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm; border-left: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-right: 0.018cm solid #000000; border-bottom: 0.018cm solid #000000\" width=\"170\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n               </table>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"TabelFod\">«</p>",
